      <title>Today’s Apps Gone Free: Metal Detector, Towaga, Discovr and More</title>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Jun 2018 13:53:09 +0000</pubDate>
      <link>http://appadvice.com/appnn/2018/06/todays-apps-gone-free-metal-detector-towaga-discovr-and-more</link>
      <guid>http://appadvice.com/appnn/2018/06/todays-apps-gone-free-metal-detector-towaga-discovr-and-more</guid>
      <description>&lt;p class="leadImageBlock" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img class="size-large aligncenter" title="Today’s Apps Gone Free: Metal Detector, Towaga, Discovr and More" src="http://wpuploads.appadvice.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/agf622018-642x321.jpg"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="overflow: hidden;"&gt;Find magnetic field generating objects, destroy monsters with beams of light, and discover new tunes with today’s collection of apps and games.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="overflow: hidden;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All app prices are subject to change at any time and without notice regardless of stated free duration. Price changes are solely under the control of the developers.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="agfDeviceHeader"&gt;iPhone:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="overflow: hidden;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://siteesi.getapp.cc/app/1159600645"&gt; &lt;img class="appIcon appIcon57" style="float: left; margin: 0px 5px 3px 0px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.746094); overflow: hidden;" src="https://is4-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple128/v4/9c/3d/5f/9c3d5fc9-e7c9-7080-a136-d10570a38933/source/60x60bb.jpg" alt="" width="57" height="57" /&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://siteesi.getapp.cc/app/1159600645"&gt; &lt;em&gt; Towaga &lt;/em&gt; &lt;/a&gt; ($0.99 → Free, 208.2 MB): Destroy monsters with beams of light in Towaga. Fans of action games.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Play as a masked sorcerer perched atop the legendary Temple of Towaga. You’re objective is to fight off the monsters lurking in the darkness using your light beam. As the monsters descend upon the temple from all angles, highlight them with your beam and release to exercise. When times get tough, unleash your super light beam to cover large swaths of enemies. The game includes six chapters in all.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Towaga&lt;/em&gt; is available for free for a limited time. It has a 4.5-star rating with a total of 28 ratings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="agfDeviceHeader"&gt;Universal:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="overflow: hidden;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://siteesi.getapp.cc/app/722921745"&gt; &lt;img class="appIcon appIcon57" style="float: left; margin: 0px 5px 3px 0px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.746094); overflow: hidden;" src="https://is2-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple125/v4/2a/d5/e7/2ad5e7c6-d839-3165-b4e4-0636938b2701/source/60x60bb.jpg" alt="" width="57" height="57" /&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://siteesi.getapp.cc/app/722921745"&gt; &lt;em&gt; Tiny Dentist Christmas &lt;/em&gt; &lt;/a&gt; ($2.99 → Free, 326.9 MB): Your child gets to play dentist and help their patients get healthy smiles with Tiny Dentist Christmas. Parents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There’s just so much to do in Tiny Dentist Christmas. It includes a vast number of colorful characters in need of some serious dental help. Your child can scroll through all of the tools at the bottom of the screen and tap on the ones that want to use like an extractor, brush, bleach, x-ray, and braces. They can also snap pictures of their patient during or after the procedure and share them on Facebook.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Tiny Dentist Christmas&lt;/em&gt; is available for free for a limited time. It has a 3.5-star rating with a total of 40 ratings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="overflow: hidden;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://siteesi.getapp.cc/app/412768094"&gt; &lt;img class="appIcon appIcon57" style="float: left; margin: 0px 5px 3px 0px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.746094); overflow: hidden;" src="https://is3-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple128/v4/66/7a/70/667a7045-37a0-3e64-1fde-75b39ee1a707/source/60x60bb.jpg" alt="" width="57" height="57" /&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://siteesi.getapp.cc/app/412768094"&gt; &lt;em&gt; Discovr &amp;#8211; discover music &lt;/em&gt; &lt;/a&gt; ($1.99 → Free, 47.8 MB): Discover new tunes to listen to based on what you already enjoy with Discovr. Those who want to expand their music library.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Start off by searching for a specific artist, or you can allow Discovr to recommend a new one or show you what&amp;#8217;s trending. From there you&amp;#8217;re able to just tap on an artist to display an interactive web of similar music. Double tap on an artist to view their bio, songs, videos, and other details. You&amp;#8217;re also able to add artists to your favorites, listen to previews, and share what you have discovered via Facebook, Twitter, or email.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Discovr &amp;#8211; discover music&lt;/em&gt; is available for free for a limited time. It has a 4.5-star rating with a total of 2804 ratings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="overflow: hidden;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://siteesi.getapp.cc/app/966179136"&gt; &lt;img class="appIcon appIcon57" style="float: left; margin: 0px 5px 3px 0px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.746094); overflow: hidden;" src="https://is5-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple118/v4/ea/a4/cb/eaa4cb46-d660-6b22-d972-9b05b5ee718e/source/60x60bb.jpg" alt="" width="57" height="57" /&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://siteesi.getapp.cc/app/966179136"&gt; &lt;em&gt; Metal Detector PRO. &lt;/em&gt; &lt;/a&gt; ($0.99 → Free, 47.3 MB): Find magnetic field generating objects with Metal Detector. Everyone from do-it-yourselfers to construction workers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Metal Detector actually works. It may not be a replacement for a professional tool, but it definitely works. Simply hold your iDevice up to any object that creates a magnetic field and Metal Detector will show its strength. The app includes the ability to adjust sensitivity and a microtesla gauge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Metal Detector PRO.&lt;/em&gt; is available for free for a limited time. It has a 2.5-star rating with a total of 22 ratings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="overflow: hidden;"&gt;That concludes today&amp;#8217;s issue of Apps Gone Free. If you like staying on top �of these daily deals, don&amp;#8217;t forget to check out our free AppsGoneFree app. &lt;a href="http://appadvice.com/link/470693788"&gt;&lt;img class="noShad" style="border-width: 0px !important; -webkit-box-shadow: none !important;" src="http://appadvice-css-image-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/AdOnPage.png" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; It provides all the deals each day, and even an archive of past deals that are still active.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Developers:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are a developer who would like to get your app included in our “Apps Gone Free” daily lists, here’s our basic set of rules:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It must have &lt;strong&gt;at least a three-star average rating&lt;/strong&gt; at the time it goes free.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The app must not have been free numerous times (3+) over the last six months.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The free version of your app must not include ads.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To submit an app, simply send a request to &lt;a href="mailto:tyler@appadvice.com?subject=Apps%20Gone%20Free"&gt;tyler@appadvice.com&lt;/a&gt; with the subject “Apps Gone Free.” Please include the name of the app, a link to it in the App Store, when and for how long you intend to offer the app for free, and anything else you would like to share. We will take it from there.&lt;/p&gt;
